text: Agdistis tsumkwe is a moth in the family Pterophoridae. It is known from South Africa and Namibia.New Species and Records of Plume Moths of the Genus Agdistis Hübner, 1825 (Lepidoptera: Pterophoridae, Agdistinae) from Southern Africa ==References== Category:Agdistinae Category:Moths of Africa Category:Insects of Namibia Category:Moths described in 2001
